### Battle log messages — en-US
### Prefix: battle

-battle-damage-dealt-text = {$source} deals {$damage} damage to {$target}
-battle-heal-received-text = {$source} restores {$value} HP to {$target}
-battle-unit-died-text = {$unit} has been defeated
-battle-critical-text = Critical hit! {$damage} damage!
-battle-miss-text = {$source} attack misses {$target}
-battle-dodge-text = {$target} dodges the attack
-battle-resist-text = {$target} resists {$effect}
-battle-counter-text = {$source} counters for {$damage} damage
-battle-immune-text = {$target} is immune to {$effect}
-battle-buff-applied-text = {$effect} applied to {$target}
-battle-buff-expired-text = {$effect} expired on {$target}
